WEBVTT

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.680
I was just passing by,

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:41.740
and came to see you.

00:01:47.039 --> 00:01:47.900
I'm doing fine.

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:51.009
Is something wrong?

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:56.210
Your favorite wontons,

00:01:56.600 --> 00:01:57.800
extra numb and spicy.

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:02.720
Let's go.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:03.160
Go in.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.200
It's been so long since I last came here.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.680
I've been too busy recently,

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:10.240
and didn't have time to visit you.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:12.000
It's also Mr. Yan's first time here, right?

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.040
He was always worried,

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:13.680
and kept saying

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.610
he wanted to come check on Guannan.

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:19.200
Why are you just standing there?

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:20.060
Come in and eat.

00:02:25.600 --> 00:02:26.240
Come in.

00:02:31.160 --> 00:02:32.880
We ordered this especially for you.

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:34.079
Extra numb and spicy.

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:03.610
I fired a shot when the killer escaped.

00:03:03.880 --> 00:03:05.880
He was at least grazed by the bullet.

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:12.180
Delicious.

00:03:13.600 --> 00:03:14.730
It's from Old Han's.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:20.040
Why so sudden today?

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:24.400
There's been a

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:26.060
serial murder case recently.

00:03:28.440 --> 00:03:29.300
Have you heard?

00:03:36.079 --> 00:03:36.560
No.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:40.160
This recent case

00:03:40.160 --> 00:03:41.960
has been driving me crazy.

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:43.240
If one day

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.490
I catch that killer,

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.329
I'll definitely interrogate him myself.

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:52.760
Eat up.

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:37.320
Oh no,

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:39.220
my clothes are all wet.

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:41.240
Why is your house leaking?

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:43.120
The plum rain season is approaching.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:46.180
You need to get the property management to check it out.

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.520
Hey, Guannan.

00:04:53.640 --> 00:04:55.100
What happened to your arm?

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:57.600
It's nothing.

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:58.980
A cat scratched it.

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.360
Let me take a look.

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:10.320
It's really nothing.

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:23.380
No need to be so polite.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.730
During rehearsals in the past,

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:28.000
didn't I always bandage your injuries?

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:37.880
What kind of cat

00:05:38.360 --> 00:05:39.760
scratched you this hard?

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:42.080
A stray cat.

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:43.920
A homeless one.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:49.930
Be more careful.

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:50.840
Make sure to

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:51.970
get a vaccine later.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:53.560
Eat up.

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:20.240
The amulet

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:21.000
was right at the door.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.600
We saw it as soon as we went in.

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:24.740
The wound on his arm

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:26.940
was right in that spot.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.930
Could it all just be a coincidence?

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:33.159
He grew up

00:06:33.159 --> 00:06:34.240
in a police family.

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:37.370
He understands police methods and logic.

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:40.490
The scariest part is

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:43.040
that he knows us.

00:06:59.360 --> 00:06:59.920
Guannan.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:02.040
Let the past decade

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:03.520
stay in the past.

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:06.250
You are a police officer's son now.

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:07.640
Remember,

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:09.810
only with a righteous heart

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:11.740
can you walk a righteous path.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:17.840
I was wrong.

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:21.920
It's too late for everything.

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:23.320
Caicai.

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:25.380
Caicai.

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:26.080
Look here.

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:26.480
Hey.

00:08:27.880 --> 00:08:28.600
Caicai.

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.240
Caicai.

00:08:37.640 --> 00:08:38.600
Caicai, look at Daddy.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.400
Look at Daddy.

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:41.919
Over here.

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:43.799
Caicai, look.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:49.160
That's all for today.

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:50.680
Thank you for your cooperation.

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:51.480
If there's any news,

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.810
notify us immediately.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:02.970
What are you drawing, baby?

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:32.800
You are the prettiest

00:09:32.960 --> 00:09:34.020
and most promising

00:09:34.120 --> 00:09:35.440
student in this class.

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:36.800
As long as you

00:09:36.840 --> 00:09:37.500
behave well

00:09:37.760 --> 00:09:38.800
and study hard,

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:40.300
you'll have

00:09:40.440 --> 00:09:41.370
a bright future.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:43.840
The only problem is

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:44.800
your lack of social experience

00:09:44.800 --> 00:09:46.000
and

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.440
life experience.

00:09:47.560 --> 00:09:48.490
But that's okay.

00:09:48.680 --> 00:09:49.760
This weekend,

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:51.480
I will invite some friends

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:52.680
from all walks of life.

00:09:52.680 --> 00:09:54.280
Let's get to know each other.

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:55.280
Come here.

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:56.440
Hold her down.

00:09:57.080 --> 00:09:57.720
Help!

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:00.400
Drink.

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:01.120
Come drink.

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:01.920
Force it down.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:02.880
Help!

00:10:20.680 --> 00:10:21.080
Dad,

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:23.720
I made this at kindergarten today.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:25.240
You made it yourself?

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:27.440
I really like it.

00:10:27.560 --> 00:10:28.040
Oh.

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:29.640
Thank you, Caicai.

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.280
Boss.

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:47.260
Give me a lollipop.

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:49.760
Um.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.300
Can I use the phone?

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:52.320
Make a call?

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:53.240
Go ahead.

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:54.040
It's free.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:07.370
Who is it?

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:10.260
Say something.

00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:12.640
If you don't speak,

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:13.370
I'll hang up.

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:40.720
Baby.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.240
At school today,

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:43.570
did you learn a new song?

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:44.560
Then,

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:45.480
sing it again for Mommy,

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:46.000
okay?

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:46.880
Okay.

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.560
I wish Daddy could hear it.

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:54.080
Twinkle, twinkle, little star,

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:58.480
How I wonder what you are.

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:03.120
Up above the world so high,

00:12:03.520 --> 00:12:07.600
Like a diamond in the sky.

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:09.000
Sing it again.

00:12:09.680 --> 00:12:13.720
Twinkle, twinkle, little star,

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:16.880
How I wonder what you...

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:21.280
Twinkle, little star,

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:25.920
How I wonder what you are.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:28.080
Up above...

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:42.570
Did you ask to see me?

00:12:54.680 --> 00:12:55.360
Captain Sun.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.480
The store owner said

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.400
he saw Liu Jiang.

00:12:57.400 --> 00:12:59.060
He headed into the mountains.

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.220
Everything Zhang Wendong did to you,

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:09.010
I have experienced too.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:11.450
I asked you to come today

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:15.360
because I don't want you to repeat my mistakes.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:19.170
I don't know what you've been through,

00:13:19.280 --> 00:13:20.080
nor do I know

00:13:20.120 --> 00:13:22.450
your relationship with Principal Zhang.

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:24.040
But he is really good to me.

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:25.840
He cares about me a lot.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:27.500
He said you had a bright future

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.520
and that you were pretty.

00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:31.560
He taught you personally, didn't he?

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:32.880
He bought you clothes

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:33.960
and jewelry.

00:13:34.240 --> 00:13:36.280
He promised to help with your career.

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:38.210
He said out of all the pretty girls,

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:39.160
he only liked you.

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:40.200
It was your honor.

00:13:40.920 --> 00:13:42.650
Since your first day at school,

00:13:42.960 --> 00:13:44.200
I've noticed you.

00:13:44.840 --> 00:13:45.960
Because you have

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:48.200
a unique beauty.

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:49.880
Especially your eyes.

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.640
There is a fragile beauty

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:53.400
in your eyes.

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:54.320
But later,

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:57.120
he slowly started to put you down.

00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:58.840
He said you were useless,

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.120
knew nothing,

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:02.520
and needed to broaden your horizons.

00:14:02.520 --> 00:14:03.400
The only problem

00:14:03.400 --> 00:14:05.960
is that you have too little social experience.

00:14:05.960 --> 00:14:07.200
I will invite some

00:14:07.280 --> 00:14:08.480
friends from various industries.

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:09.560
Get to know each other

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:10.560
and communicate more.

00:14:10.560 --> 00:14:11.490
That'll be fine.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:14.640
He started taking you to network

00:14:14.640 --> 00:14:16.520
and to various entertainment venues.

00:14:16.520 --> 00:14:17.160
He introduced you

00:14:17.160 --> 00:14:18.400
to different men.

00:14:19.760 --> 00:14:21.290
He made you entertain them.

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:22.800
If you didn't,

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:25.200
he would threaten you with those photos.

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.240
Stop talking.

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:28.370
Did you ask me here just to say this?

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:30.100
What exactly do you want to do?

00:14:32.760 --> 00:14:34.160
I want to help you.

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:42.450
I didn't have the chance to save myself back then.

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:44.560
But you do.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.920
You can even save more girls,

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:48.960
including me.

00:14:54.920 --> 00:14:56.080
Zhang Wendong still

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:57.680
trusts you now, right?

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.960
Did he, to express his unique love,

00:15:00.960 --> 00:15:01.440
give you

00:15:02.320 --> 00:15:03.720
the key to his office?

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.130
Did he give it to you?

00:15:07.080 --> 00:15:08.480
He hides all those photos

00:15:08.680 --> 00:15:10.160
in his office.

00:15:29.960 --> 00:15:31.880
We'll be seeing each other again,

00:15:32.440 --> 00:15:33.680
Principal Zhang.